DS4_MTP_TIMING decomposition (K=2):
  draft (MTP forward):          ~6 ms / token
  verify-batch-2 (n_tok=2):     ~120 ms (1.9x baseline ~63 ms decode)
  margin-skip 1-tok verify:     ~62 ms (== baseline)
